      <title>德国将向 OHB 订购价值 21 亿欧元的卫星</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/germany-to-place-2-1-billion-satellites-order-with-ohb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德国计划从 OHB SE 购买三颗卫星，用于其武装部队，订单价值为 21 亿欧元（23 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/germany-to-place-2-1-billion-satellites-order-with-ohb</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 15:32:24 GMT</pubDate>
